    public final class Under<S,T,A,B>
extends Object
implements Fn3<Iso<S,T,A,B>,Function<? super T,? extends S>,B,A>
    The inverse of Over: given an Iso, a function from T to S, and a "smaller" value B, return a "smaller" value A by traversing around the type ring (B -> T -> S -> A).

    Note this is only possible for Isos and not general LensLikes because of the mandatory need for the correspondence B -> T.
